    "Similarly, AI researchers have outlined principles and ethics frameworks for responsible AI by means of participatory research (i.e., human and user-centred design, which are sensitive to the values of all stakeholders.",
    "PPI values also help ensure AI interfaces are accessible for non-experts, prioritising stakeholder input in co-creating AI models, while considering fairness, accountability, and transparency) [84, 85].",
    "This has wide-ranging applications in healthcare too.",
